"title": "6708: predestination",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6708",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's foreordination of all events and circumstances for the good of his people and the glory of his name.</p>\n<h2>Predestination depends on God's sovereignty</h2>\n<h3>He is the Creator of all things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17-Jer32:19\">JER 32:17–32:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:1-Job38:4\">JOB 38:1–38:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:24-Isa44:28\">ISA 44:24–44:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:12-Isa45:13\">ISA 45:12–45:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:12-Isa48:14\">ISA 48:12–48:14</a></p>\n<h3>He rules over nature and history</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:4\">PRO 16:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:10-Gen18:14\">GEN 18:10–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:4\">PSA 67:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:9\">PRO 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:33\">PRO 16:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:1\">PRO 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:23-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:23–8:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:35-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:35–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:22-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:22–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29-Matt10:30\">MAT 10:29–10:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></p>\n<h3>His will is perfect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:3\">JOB 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:137\">PSA 119:137</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:37\">DAN 4:37</a></p>\n<h2>God's predestined purposes cannot be thwarted</h2>\n<h3>Human beings cannot stand against his will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:19-Rom9:21\">ROM 9:19–9:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:4\">PSA 2:1–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:30\">PRO 21:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24-Isa14:27\">ISA 14:24–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10-Isa46:12\">ISA 46:10–46:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:35\">DAN 4:35</a></p>\n<h3>False gods are impotent before him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:3-Ps115:8\">PSA 115:3–115:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:8–44:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:20\">ISA 45:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:14\">ISA 48:14</a></p>\n<h3>He brings good out of evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:20\">GEN 50:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:13-Gen15:16\">GEN 15:13–15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:4-Gen45:8\">GEN 45:4–45:8</a></p>\n<h2>Predestination undergirds biblical prophecy</h2>\n<h3>It explains the prophets' confidence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:17-1Kgs22:28\">1KI 22:17–22:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10-1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:10–1:12</a></p>\n<h3>It is demonstrated in the fulfilment of prophecy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:29-1Kgs22:38\">1KI 22:29–22:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:22\">MAT 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:15\">MAT 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:23\">MAT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:14\">MAT 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:17-Matt12:19\">MAT 12:17–12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:25\">ACT 2:17–2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:22-Acts3:25\">ACT 3:22–3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:27-Acts13:30\">ACT 13:27–13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:15-Acts15:18\">ACT 15:15–15:18</a></p>\n<h2>The life and ministry of Jesus Christ was predestined</h2>\n<h3>In that it was predicted by the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">ISA 9:6–9:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:10\">ISA 11:1–11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">ISA 52:13–53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5-Jer23:6\">JER 23:5–23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a></p>\n<h3>In his sufferings and death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:32\">LUK 18:31–18:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:22\">LUK 22:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25-Luke24:27\">LUK 24:25–24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44-Luke24:45\">LUK 24:44–24:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:30\">ACT 4:27–4:30</a></p>\n<h3>In the outcome it achieved</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's purpose in predestination is to bless his people</h2>\n<h3>In the path their lives follow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:14-Ps139:16\">PSA 139:14–139:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11\">JER 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29-Matt10:31\">MAT 10:29–10:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:6-Luke12:7\">LUK 12:6–12:7</a></p>\n<h3>In their salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:29–8:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:1–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:27\">MAT 11:25–11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11\">MRK 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:37-John6:44\">JHN 6:37–6:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>In their assurance of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:31–8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:29\">JHN 10:27–10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2\">JHN 17:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:3–1:14</a> <em>Predestination is basic to Christian certainty.</em></p>\n<h3>Regarding final perseverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:8\">PSA 138:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:37-John6:40\">JHN 6:37–6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>Regarding God's call to righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:4-Jer1:5\">JER 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:10\">ACT 22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:17\">GAL 1:15–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Regarding future inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:30\">ROM 8:30</a></p>\n<h2>God predestines judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:11-Isa65:12\">ISA 65:11–65:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:17\">GEN 6:17</a> <em>the flood</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:13\">EXO 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:13-Exod9:18\">EXO 9:13–9:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:20\">JOS 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:25-2Kgs19:26\">2KI 19:25–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24-Isa14:27\">ISA 14:24–14:27</a> <em>judgment on Assyria</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:12-Isa19:14\">ISA 19:12–19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">ISA 23:9</a> <em>judgment on Tyre</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:20\">JER 49:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:45\">JER 50:45</a> <em>judgment on Babylon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:6–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14-Isa8:15\">ISA 8:14–8:15</a></p>\n<h2>Predestination does not set aside human responsibility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:37\">JHN 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a></p>",
